     <div id="achievements"> 
      <h2></h2> 
      <br> 
      <p><img src="images/ocdsflagorg.jpg" width="211" height="140"><br> </p> 
      <br> 
      <p><strong>"To provide strategic directions and develop joint doctrine for the Armed Forces in Sri Lanka."</strong></p> 
      <div class="clear"></div> 
     </div> 
     <hr> 
     <div id="achievements1"> 
      <h2></h2> 
      <p class="subtitle">OCDS Latest, Special &amp; Other News. </p>
      <p class="subtitle"><img width="158" height="106" src="images/news/news127/05.JPG" align="left" hspace="12"></p> 
      <p align="justify" id="ach_text"><span class="headline"> NEW DIRECTOR GENERAL OF THE CIVIL SECURITY DEPARTMENT CALLS ON THE CDS </span> Newly appointed Director General of the Civil Security Department (CSD), Mr Chandraratne Pallegama called on General Jagath Jayasuriya, the Chief of Defence Staff (CDS) on 20th afternoon at the CDS Office at BMICH. </p> 
      <div class="clear"></div> 
      <ul class="btn_more"> 
       <li><a href="news127.php" title="read more">More</a></li> 
      </ul> 
      <br> 
      <hr> 
      <p class="subtitle"><img width="158" height="106" src="images/news/news126/01.jpg" align="left" hspace="12"></p> 
      <p align="justify" id="ach_text"><span class="headline"> STATE MINISTER VISITS TRINCOMALEE NAVAL INSTALLATION </span> During his visit to the Eastern region the Sate Minster of Defence Hon. Ruwan Wijewardene visited the Sri Lanka Navy installation in Trincomalee on the 08th (February 2015). </p> 
      <div class="clear"></div> 
      <ul class="btn_more"> 
       <li><a href="news126.php" title="read more">More</a></li> 
      </ul> 
      <br> 
      <hr> 
      <p class="subtitle"><img width="158" height="106" src="images/news/news125/04.jpg" align="left" hspace="12"></p> 
      <p align="justify" id="ach_text"><span class="headline"> MINISTER WIJEWARDENE VISITS WANNI TROOPS </span> State Minister of Defence Hon. Ruwan Wijewardene who is presently on an official visit to the Northern Military establishments, arrived at the Security Forces Headquarters Wanni (SFHQ-Wanni) today (7th Feb). </p> 
      <div class="clear"></div> 
      <ul class="btn_more"> 
       <li><a href="news125.php" title="read more">More</a></li> 
      </ul> 
      <br> 
      <hr> 
      <p class="subtitle"><img width="158" height="106" src="images/news/news124/01.jpg" align="left" hspace="12"></p> 
      <p align="justify" id="ach_text"><span class="headline"> MINISTER WIJEWARDENE ARRIVES IN KILINOCHCHI </span> On successful completion of Northern visit, State Minister of Defence Hon. Ruwan Wijewardene arrived at the Security Forces Headquarters Kilinochchi (SFHQ-KLN) today (7th Feb).</p> 
      <div class="clear"></div> 
      <ul class="btn_more"> 
       <li><a href="news124.php" title="read more">More</a></li> 
      </ul> 
      <br> 
      <hr> 
      <p class="subtitle"><img width="158" height="106" src="images/news/news123/06.jpg" align="left" hspace="12"></p> 
      <p align="justify" id="ach_text"><span class="headline"> MINISTER WIJEWARDENE VISITS NORTHERN PROVINCE </span> The State Minister of Defence Hon. Ruwan Wijewardene arrived at the Northern Province while commencing his first official visit to the Military Establishments today (6th Feb). Chief of Defence Staff, Tri-Forces Commanders, Security Forces Commander - Jaffna and the regional heads of respective forces welcomed the Minister on his arrival at the Palaly Air Port. </p> 
      <div class="clear"></div> 
      <ul class="btn_more"> 
       <li><a href="news123.php" title="read more">More</a></li> 
      </ul> 
      <br> 
      <hr> 
      <p class="subtitle"><img width="158" height="106" src="images/news/news122/01.JPG" align="left" hspace="12"></p> 
      <p align="justify" id="ach_text"><span class="headline"> CDS CALLS ON THE PRIME MINISTER </span> General Jagath Jayasuriya, Chief of Defence Staff called on Hon Ranil wickremesinghe, the Prime Minister of Sri Lanka on 27 January 2015 at the Temple Trees, Colombo. The Chief of Defence Staff briefed Hon Prime Minister about the security situation and the functions of the Office of the Chief of Defence Staff.</p> 
      <div class="clear"></div> 
      <ul class="btn_more"> 
       <li><a href="news122.php" title="read more">More</a></li> 
      </ul> 
