      <ul class="btn_more"> 
       <li><a href="news9.php" title="read more">More</a></li> 
      </ul> 
      <br> 
      <hr> 
      <p class="subtitle"><img src="images/news/IMG_7427.jpg" width="148" class="magnify" height="105" alt=""></p> 
      <p align="justify" id="ach_text"><span class="headline">US GOVERNMENT DELEGATION CALLS ON CDS. </span>The Deputy Assistant Secretary of Defence of United States of America Mr. Vikram Singh called on Chief of Defence Staff Air Chief Marshal Roshan Goonetileke RWP &amp; bar, VSV,USP,ndc,psc on 28 January 2013 at the OCDS. He was accompanied by the US Defence Attaché in Sri Lanka, Lieutenant Colonel Patrik Schuler.</p> 
      <div class="clear"></div> 
      <br> 
      <hr> 
      <p class="subtitle"><img src="images/news/news12/1.JPG" width="148" class="magnify" height="105" alt=""></p> 
      <p align="justify" id="ach_text"><span class="headline">CDS VISITS INDIA. </span>The Chief of Defence Staff, Air Chief Marshal Roshan Goonetileke along with a high level defence delegation, visited India from 22 to 26 January 2013.</p> 
      <div class="clear"></div> 
      <ul class="btn_more"> 
       <li><a href="news12.php" title="read more">More</a></li> 
      </ul> 
      <br> 
      <hr> 
      <p class="subtitle"><img src="images/news/IMG_7440.jpg" width="148" class="magnify" height="105" alt=""></p> 
      <p align="justify" id="ach_text"><span class="headline">Parliamentary Delegation of Australia meets Sri Lankan Defence Officials at the OCDS. </span>A Parliamentary Delegation of Australia led by Hon. Julie Bishop MP, Deputy Leader of Opposition met with Chief of Defence Staff Air Chief Marshal WDRMJ Goonetileke and held discussions on 31 December 2012 at the Office of the Chief of Defence Staff.</p> 
      <br> 
      <p align="justify" id="ach_text1">Hon. Scott Morrison MP, Hon. Michael Keenan MP, along with the Australian High Commissioner for Sri Lanka, Her Excellency Ms. Robyn Mudie accompanied the Australian Deputy Leader of Opposition at this event. The Commander of the Navy, Inspector General of Police, Chief of National Intelligence and Deputy Director Coast Guard joined the Chief of Defence Staff at this bilateral meeting.</p> 
      <div class="clear"></div> 
      <br> 
